= rprov

== Description

rprov is a tool for managing your Eclipse instance.

== FEATURES/PROBLEMS:

* The tool can determine the status of an Eclipse instance or a single plugin
* There is no way to install bundles for now.
* The diagnosis is franly quite bare.

== SYNOPSIS:

Run the rprov script in the bin folder.
./rprov help
./rprov st -e /path/to/eclipse
./rprov st -e /path/to/eclipse org.eclipse.ui

== Installation

* sudo gem install intalio-rprov

